    ],
    chronologyEn: [
      'Horus reaches manhood and claims his father\'s throne before the tribunal of the gods.',
      'Ra rejects Horus\'s claim and the trial drags on for decades.',
      'Isis disguises herself as a widow and tricks Set into unknowingly endorsing Horus\'s right.',
      'Horus and Set battle through various contests, including as hippopotamuses and in physical combat.',
      'Set schemes to degrade Horus through trickery, but the plan backfires and disgraces Set instead.',
