    ],
    chronologyEn: [
      'The soul crosses the Duat, passing gates and guardians with the aid of spells from the Book of the Dead.',
      'The soul arrives at the Hall of Two Truths before Osiris and the forty-two judges.',
      'The soul recites the Negative Confession, declaring sins it never committed.',
      'Anubis places the soul\'s heart on one side of the scale and the feather of Ma\'at on the other.',
